high_descs: turn left and walk around over to the kitchen stove
grab a pan off of the back left burning on the stove
turn around and walk over to the fridge
place the pan inside of the fridge and let it cool off, then take it back out
turn right and head over to the kitchen sink
place the pan down in the corner of the kitchen counter left of the toaster
anns.task_desc: place a cooled pan down on the kitchen counter corner

high_descs: Turn left towards the edge of the table, then turn right towards the stove.
Pick up the metal bowl on the stove.
Turn around and head towards the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the bowl on the top shelf, close the fridge and wait for the bowl to cool, open the fridge and get the bowl from it.
Turn left and head towards the toaster on the counter.
Place the bowl to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place the cool bowl next to the toaster on the counter.

high_descs: Go to the stove to your left.
Pick up the pot on the back left stove top.
Go to the fridge behind you.
Chill the pot in the fridge.
Go to the counter to your left, near the sink.
Place the pot on the counter to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pot on the counter.
